description: Does healthy FAST FOOD exist??? In today’s episode, Lisa answers this question… Plus, she has the TOP ways to save 100 calories at the drive-thru, 3 ways to make healthy fries, supermarket must-haves for an at-home burger fix, and surprising things to completely AVOID at the fast-food counter! This episode made us so full that we had to do another! Stay tuned for FAST FOOD Part 2… Coming up next week! [hungry-girl.com/fastfood](hungry-girl.com/fastfood)
